title: This 6-Year-Old Girl's 'Selena' Themed Birthday Party Is EVERYTHING | Fred And Angi | 100.3 Kiss FM
text:
share 
This is so amazing! 
6 year-old Ayvah just had the most amazing birthday party. Probably the youngest Selena fan ever, she discovered her love for the late singer through videos of the singer on YouTube and instantly became obsessed with Selena's dance moves. 
Ayvah's mom spent months preparing the most epic Selena-themed birthday party for her daughter, which included the perfect cake and a Selena piñata.
